results.title: Orson Scott Card's Speaker for the Dead #2
results.description: The award-winning novel comes to life as the saga of Ender Wiggin continues! Ender is called to a distant planet to speak the death of a scientist brutally murdered by a mysterious alien species. But instead of uncovering the truth, Ender finds a web of lies and deceit that threatens to endanger the entire planet. Based on the novel by bestselling author Orson Scott Card.

results.title: Ka-Zar (2010) #4
results.description: Four separate lives intersect as a terrible natural disaster threatens to devastate the Savage Land. Ka-Zar makes his play against an unseen enemy, a courageous Tribal leader must stand against everything he knows and visit the outside world, knowing that failure will result in the collapse of all Pangean society. For this is a war won not with might but with words...
